LINUX INSTRUCTIONS
------------------

To install `New Hope`, follow these steps:

  1. Install, if not already installed:
    a. zlib library <http://www.zlib.net/>
    b. PNG library <http://www.libpng.org/pub/libpng.html>
    c. SDL library <http://www.libsdl.org/>
    d. SDL_ttf library <http://www.libsdl.org/projects/SDL_ttf/>
  2. Edit config.mk to adapt settings to your system (usually not needed)
  3. Run `make`
  4. Run `make install` with administrator privileges

That's it. Now just type `newhope` to run the game.
